<note n="0264001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0264001">此句之意若依註，言我見或聞第一波羅夷事。後受詢問，則言我不見不聞，乃前後所說有相違也。其次失壞、犯罪意亦同。</note>
<note n="0264002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0264002">原語 vaṇṇāvaṇṇa，言精有種種色，第一僧殘也，言以下順次至第五僧殘。</note>
<note n="0264003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0264003">dhanamanuppadānaṁ，言第五僧殘，媒嫁戒。</note>
<note n="0268004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0268004">此頌意義，參照十一呵責品註[01]。</note>
